r-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><section style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">李月亮<span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">&nbsp;☽<\/span><\/span><\/section><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但谢霆锋的国籍，确实有点复杂。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">按照粉丝们给出的说法，谢霆锋是1980年出生的，移民时间应该是在1987年前后。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那时香港还没有回归，属于英国殖民时期，他应该是获得了加拿大国籍，但仍然保留了居港权，也就是所谓的“双重国籍”。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而现在，谢霆锋虽然退掉了加拿大国籍，但他还有香港永久居民的身份，所以他仍然是中国人，不需要重新加入中国籍。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; padding-right: 0.5em; padding-left: 0.5em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/199e0da46aff3c4901439116f792a118.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; text-align: center; box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过，咱们国家的《国籍法》有明确规定，不承认中国公民具有双重国籍。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以翻看谢霆锋以往的影视作品、歌曲MV等，就会发现，他的名字旁一直备注的都是“中国香港”。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/9b3ba808c891029d52d1def8aa0c3662.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">建党100周年金曲《百年》MV截图<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而客观说，谢霆锋在国家立场上，表现也一直不错。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那首大部分人都会唱的《黄种人》，就是他根据自己在外留学的感受，亲自填词创作的，很正：<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">越动荡 越勇敢<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">留下属于我的黄<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一身坦荡荡<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">黄天在上<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">看我如何做好汉<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2003年10月，非典刚过，他还曾在北京的万人演唱会上说：<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“在我们中国的<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">历史来看，更难抗、更难受的时间，我们也熬得过去。”<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/4a009a7f8a18d04dfcff6d464cc6e9ae.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以，谢霆锋说他自己爱国，我倒是不怀疑。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不过问题来了，正如网友质疑：香港回归已经24年了，<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">他为何早不退晚不退，偏偏现在退呢？<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这背后，可能有爱国心，但，一定更有利益衡量。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 50px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">03<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><section style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">李月亮<span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">&nbsp;☽<\/span><\/span><\/section><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">很多人可能不知道，谢霆锋除了是演员、歌手以外，还有一个身份——青年企业家。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前，他的商业版图所涉及的行业有：娱乐、影视、服装、餐饮、房地产……可以说是遍地开花。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这几年，很多人嘲笑他不务正业，一心只想当厨子。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">殊不知他创立的品牌“锋味”，每年都有2个多亿的流水，算是闷声发大财了。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/adade8e86bdb94aaf7db9db2b77d26f7.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2012年，谢霆锋受邀去香港科技大学做讲座时，就曾说过这样一句话：<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“我把所有的精力和资金，首先都放在了我们的祖国——中国。”<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/d46d00101eff57713ce837abe201ce6e.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 546px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">他也确实是这么做的。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">他入股投资的连锁酒吧，开在上海、杭州、长沙、郑州……<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">他名下相关联的几家公司，注册地是上海、天津、深圳、青岛……<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">他出品并制作的综艺节目，在浙江台播出。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，他还是国货品牌“特步”的股东。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">也就是说，无论作为艺人，还是作为商人，谢霆锋的事业重心都在内地。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我想，这样的商业部署，可能是因为爱国。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但更主要的原因，肯定还是内地的市场更大、机会更多，更容易赚钱。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以从实际出发，对于现在的谢霆锋来说，加拿大国籍不仅用处不大，还会带来一些负面争议。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而中国人的身份，才是真香。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 50px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">04<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><section style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">李月亮<span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">&nbsp;☽<\/span><\/span><\/section><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">事实上，谢霆锋并非第一个公开宣布退出外国国籍的公众人物。<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">今年7月份，青年演员陈飞宇，就是陈凯歌和陈红的儿子，就在微博上公开声明，出生于美国的他，正式放弃美国国籍，成为一名中国公民。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/05b63f20824d93911341b6d41ab23202.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 650px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">更早一点的，还有2岁时随父母移民的甄子丹。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2013年，他在杨澜的访谈节目里说：<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“四年前我就把美国籍给退了，我现在是百分之百中国籍的人。”<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/4bc9b3178b63f27a2416dc4e8552ad94.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 624px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">很多人都说，他们放弃外国籍，选择中国籍，无非是利益考量<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">不是因为多爱国，而是在中国赚钱多<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我倒是觉得，就算是利益衡量，也无可厚非。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">说到底大家都是俗人<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">其实他们初心如何也不重要。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们更应该看到的是，明星们的选择，证明<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">今日之中国，真的越来越强，越来越有吸<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">引力了。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">除了明星，这些年选择回国的海外华人也越来越多了。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">人社部两年前就曾说：<strong style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我国正在出现历史上最大规模的留学人员归国潮。<\/strong><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">2009<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">年，选择回中国的留学人员还不到11万，而10年后的2019年，这个数字就猛增到了58万，翻了5倍还多。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">到2020年，因为疫情影响，海归人数更是暴增。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">那人们为什么回国呢？<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">《2020中国海归就业创业调查报告》显示，留学生决定回国的理由前四位分别是：<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国内疫情控制得好。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国内生活更便利。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国内经济恢复更好。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国内就业机会更多。<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; padding-right: 0.5em; padding-left: 0.5em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/e9ea812fc970427e8accb7786b499da8.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0em 0em 0.5em 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 553px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">总之，就是因为中国生活好，发展空间大，大家才选择回来。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这真的挺说明问题。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">回想当年，上世纪八九十年代，在很多中国人心里，出国念个书是不得了的事情。<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">能拿到美国绿卡，哇，太骄傲了。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">能定居海外，简直梦寐以求。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">咱也不能说这种心态不对。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因为那时很多国家的生活，就是比中国好。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而人性都是趋利避害的。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“因为一颗爱国心，选择回到穷困的祖国”，这是闪光的人格。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">更多的人，还是普通人：爱国，但也想过更好的生活，所以哪里过得好，就留在哪里。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">可喜的是，短短三四十年，情况就发生了翻天覆地的变化。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">越来越多的海外华人，愿意因为“在中国生活更好”，而回到祖国。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这很值得骄傲。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 50px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">05<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><section style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">李月亮<span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">&nbsp;☽<\/span><\/span><\/section><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">你可能也听过这句话：我们所处的这个时代，正在经历百年未有之大变局。<\/span><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">尤其是作为中国人，我们曾经有过世界之巅的辉煌，也经历过山河破碎的绝望。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">我们是带着民族的衰败和列强的侵略，迈入20世纪的。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但也就是在这100年里，一代又一代中国人，前赴后继，艰苦奋斗，<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">让这个积贫积弱的国家，重新站了起来。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">100年前，中国和西方相差近200年。<\/span><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">40年前，中国和西方相差近50年。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而现在，我们的距离已经越来越近了。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">来看1900年，美国俄亥俄州的一个街景：<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/591fc7dbf7cc0aeb60e5ca7daf390c8e.png\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">俨<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">然已经有了现代化城市的样子。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而中国1900年的“皇城第一门”——北京大清门，还是这样：<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/8e109eb110763bd664a98a2db465942c.png\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 590px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">到了1970年，美国已经高楼大厦、汽车洋房：<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&