izing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">为什么那时候很多人说“外国的月亮比中国圆”呢？<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因为很多西方发达国家，就是比我们先进，比我们富裕啊。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在这样的差距下，人们想去美国发展，也可以理解。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">好在，在落后的日子里，我们中国人不只在“崇洋”，更在发奋建设祖国。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在一代又一代中国人的努力下，现在，我们<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">和发达国家的差<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">距<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">，已经肉眼可见地缩小了<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这是2020年的纽约时代广场，很繁华：<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/55258db90d5eab3e64eb6084e34a3332.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这是我们上海的夜景，也不差：<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/4448db985d7e01c9ef4d524a8369f386.jpeg\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">一百年，在历史的长河里只是一瞬。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但对中国来说，真是换了人间。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1970年以前，大部分国人的日常，还是煤油灯、劈柴、生炉子、挑水、缝衣服、吃咸菜……<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">而现在，我们的生活已经是天然气、智能<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">手机、网购、外卖、高铁、旅行……<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这在四十年前，都是想都不敢想的东西啊<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" src=\"http:\/\/img.youshu.cc\/readwith\/20210910\/2d957d05e1b24b58912d0a3bddd4a865.png\" alt=\"图片\" style=\"outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important; width: 677px !important; visibility: visible !important;\"\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 50px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">06<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><section style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">李月亮<span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\">&nbsp;☽<\/span><\/span><\/section><section style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(187, 51, 38); font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.5px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) 0px 0px 0px !important;\"><br\/><\/span><\/span><\/section><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">更好的消息是，我们前进的脚步仍在继续。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果你常看新闻就会发现，这几年，有很多与老百姓息息相关的大事。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">比如，就在今年，中国完成了脱贫攻坚战。<\/span><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这是世界上规模最大、力度最强的脱贫攻坚战，我们用8年的时间，就让近1亿人摆脱了绝对贫困，对世界减贫贡献率超过70%。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">然后，国家开始下一盘更大的棋——共同富裕。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">目前，我国人民的收入状况是这样的：低收入人群数量有9亿多，中等收入人群是4亿，高收入人群为几千万。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大部分人还是低收入。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">国家计划，到2035年，中等收入人群的数量，要从现有的4亿变成8亿。<\/span><br\/><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">——就是说，让大部分人都赚得更多，生活更好。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">此外，<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">还有很多一直困扰普通人的问题，国家也在一项一项重拳整治：<\/span><\/section><\/p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-left: 16px; padding-left: 2.2em; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><li><p style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">房产去金融化，控制房价。<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">医疗去市场化，让老百姓看得起病。<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">教育去资本化，为孩子和家长减负。<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">明<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">确宣布996违法，从政策上拯救“打工人”。<\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br\/><\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">大力整治娱乐圈，让偶像真正成为正向榜样。<\/span><\/p><\/li><li><p style=\"margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">……<\/span><\/p><\/li><\/ul><p><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">发现没，国家方方面面都在出手，尽力铲除各种大山，让老百姓的日子越来越好。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">虽然很多问题极其复杂，极难解决。<br\/><\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">但是只要国家有决心，一切就大有希望。<\/span><\/section><section style=\"white-space: normal; margin-right: 16px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 16px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.5440000295639038px; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><\/span><span style=\"outline: 0px; max-width: